Title: Einhell TE-AP 950 E All Purpose Reciprocating Saw Recip 240V 950W + KWB Blade
Description:
The Einhell TE-AP 950 E universal saw is designed for high-precision cutting results on wood, plastic and metal.
A powerful 950 W rating and electronic stroke speed control enable the tool to be adjusted to each particular material and application.
The tool can therefore be perfectly adjusted to different materials, material thicknesses and jobs.
The cutting depth in wood is 0.2 m and in steel 0.02 m.
The soleplate can be adjusted without any tools to make optimum use of the blade.
The saw blade can be changed quickly without the need for any tools.
The universal saw lies comfortably in the hand thanks to the large soft grip area, which makes it comfortable and above all safe to work with.
It was developed with an ergonomic and slimline design in mind to make it easy to handle.

The product is supplied complete with a KWB quality saw blade for wood.
 
Features 

Electronic stroke speed control for adjusting to application
Soleplate adjustable without tools for optimum blade use
Blade change without tools
Large soft grip area for comfortable and safe operation
Ergonomic, slim design for easy handling
